{
  "title": "Intense Juicy Kenyan Beef Skewers",
  "description": "Pungent and juicy Kenyan beef skewers served with fries and beurre-monte, perfect for a date night, this dish is kosher-friendly and cooked on a comal.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
  "diet": [
